49
00:03:34,319 --> 00:03:34,919
Right?

50
00:03:34,919 --> 00:03:35,419
Yes.

51
00:03:35,419 --> 00:03:36,020
Look at you.

52
00:03:36,020 --> 00:03:37,319
At this age, after all.

53
00:03:37,439 --> 00:03:38,099
Right.

54
00:03:38,099 --> 00:03:39,020
At this age, after all,

55
00:03:39,020 --> 00:03:40,759
