68
00:04:03,659 --> 00:04:04,340
I...

69
00:04:05,979 --> 00:04:06,780
Dad.

70
00:04:07,259 --> 00:04:08,819
I've wanted to tell you for a long time.

71
00:04:09,259 --> 00:04:09,960
You...

72
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:10,659
You...

73
00:04:14,060 --> 00:04:17,779
You still don't pay enough attention to your health.

74
00:04:17,899 --> 00:04:20,060
