00:19:45,359 --> 00:19:46,759
The seniors are all very lovely.

589
00:19:47,279 --> 00:19:48,559
Happy as brothers and sisters.

590
00:19:48,559 --> 00:19:49,519
Like big children.

591
00:19:50,000 --> 00:19:50,799
To be honest...

592
00:19:50,799 --> 00:19:52,440
When I retire one day...

593
00:19:52,440 --> 00:19:54,279
I'd also like to spend my golden years here.

594
00:19:54,279 --> 00:19:55,680
And become one of them.

595
00:19:56,500 --> 00:19:57,519
You're welcome to.

596
00:19:58,799 --> 00:19:59,599
President Li.

597
00:19:59,680 --> 00:20:01,440
I'll ask Mr. Zhao to bring the car around.

598
00:20:01,440 --> 00:20:02,119
Good.

599
00:20:02,359 --> 00:20:03,400
President Li, I'll let you get back to work.

600
00:20:03,440 --> 00:20:04,519
I'm going to take off my makeup.

601
00:20:04,519 --> 00:20:04,920
Okay.

602
00:20:04,920 --> 00:20:05,839
Goodbye.

603
00:20:20,599 --> 00:20:21,519
Who says?

604
00:20:21,599 --> 00:20:22,440
You say.

605
00:20:22,440 --> 00:20:23,279
You say.

606
00:20:23,279 --> 00:20:23,920
You say.

607
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:24,519
You say.

608
00:20:24,519 --> 00:20:25,519
Fine, I'll say.

609
00:20:26,519 --> 00:20:28,200
Actually, you say.

610
00:20:28,359 --> 00:20:29,319
Why?

611
00:20:29,519 --> 00:20:31,119
Dad spoils his daughter the most.

612
00:20:31,119 --> 00:20:33,039
Bad news coming from a daughter's mouth

613
00:20:33,039 --> 00:20:34,599
is easier for Dad to accept.

614
00:20:39,640 --> 00:20:41,599
Forgot to turn off the kitchen stove again.

615
00:20:41,599 --> 00:20:42,400
Honestly.

616
00:20:42,440 --> 00:20:43,240
Come back.

617
00:20:45,960 --> 00:20:46,759
What?

618
00:20:47,160 --> 00:20:48,039
The phone.

619
00:20:48,480 --> 00:20:49,839
Who's sending you WeChats?

620
00:20:50,400 --> 00:20:51,200
This...

621
00:20:51,759 --> 00:20:52,759
Who is it?

622
00:20:55,720 --> 00:20:57,440
Honey, I've told you a hundred times.

623
00:20:57,440 --> 00:20:59,920
That's just a normal female classmate.

624
00:21:00,839 --> 00:21:01,680
Female bestie.

625
00:21:02,000 --> 00:21:02,799
What?

626
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:04,480
You even have a female bestie?

627
00:21:04,720 --> 00:21:05,559
You're allowed a male bestie,

628
00:21:05,559 --> 00:21:06,960
but I can't have a female bestie?

629
00:21:07,440 --> 00:21:08,400
Wu Yuntang.

630
00:21:08,400 --> 00:21:08,980
You...

631
00:21:08,980 --> 00:21:13,279
Look, The east wind sweeps ten thousand miles, vast and majestic.

632
00:21:13,279 --> 00:21:16,460
The east wind sweeps ten thousand miles, vast and majestic.

633
00:21:16,460 --> 00:21:18,559
Dad, you're in a good mood.

634
00:21:18,799 --> 00:21:20,680
Joy refreshes the spirit.

635
00:21:21,039 --> 00:21:21,759
Go to the kitchen

636
00:21:21,759 --> 00:21:23,599
and get that bottle of Maotai Old Fu gave me.

637
00:21:25,680 --> 00:21:27,279
What's the happy occasion?

638
00:21:27,279 --> 00:21:28,480
Nothing much really.

639
00:21:29,799 --> 00:21:30,720
Why are you standing there not moving?

640
00:21:30,720 --> 00:21:31,039
Why are you standing there not moving?

641
00:21:31,039 --> 00:21:31,680
Go.

642
00:21:31,680 --> 00:21:32,200
Dad.

643
00:21:32,200 --> 00:21:33,359
If you have nothing to say,

644
00:21:33,839 --> 00:21:34,920
I have something to say.

645
00:21:34,920 --> 00:21:35,599
You...

646
00:21:35,599 --> 00:21:37,099
Didn't you tell me to say it?

647
00:21:37,099 --> 00:21:37,420
I...

648
00:21:37,480 --> 00:21:38,279
Dad.

649
00:21:38,359 --> 00:21:40,039
The company asked me to formally notify you

650
00:21:40,039 --> 00:21:42,140
to process your retirement procedures.
